      "description": "This car is being offered honestly as a poor-condition project, repair candidate, or parts car. It shows significant overall wear and should not be mistaken for a clean driver-quality example. Expect cosmetic deterioration inside and out, deferred maintenance, and the likelihood that it will need substantial mechanical sorting before it can be considered dependable. Best suited for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at and is prepared for ongoing work rather than a buyer seeking something turnkey.",
